name: Cosmic Freedom
description: Inspired by "The Unicorn in Captivity" (...)the unicorn probably represents the beloved tamed. He is tethered to a tree and constrained by a fence, but the chain is not secure and the fence is low enough to leap over: The unicorn could escape if he wished." Sagittarius loves being in love but they hate being captured. Fourth of the Venus in Sagittarius series. 2021
